{"tid":1679294,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【恥笑，TVB連累廣告商】今日洗版任務 - 鈣思健","createTime":"2019-10-28T06:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T04:20:41.000Z","uid":113630,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"933bcbda9940c0dbfafe0c08babccd8134ddab76","tid":1679294,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>轟炸電郵任務，#2 有詳細點人數</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第3️⃣批電郵：167 --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>179人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第4️⃣批電郵：133 --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>147人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(請補做：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PkEVlb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PkEVlb&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5yZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=287ff7ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PkEVlb</a>)<br />\n<blockquote>如果email打晒回頭、或者Gmail唔俾send<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. 轉email title<br />\n2. 轉用Yahoo / Hotmail<br />\n3. 電郵title隔空格，請自行創作：強 烈 要 求 不 與 無 綫 電 視 簽 訂 廣 告 合 約<br />\n4. 電郵內容隔空格<br />\nTemplate - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/mJvbgkX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/mJvbgkX</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每日洗版行動，真係work ga！<br />\nBless 上星期回應網民洗版</span></strong></span><br />\n喺TVB落廣告就係有咁嘅risk，本來醜聞冇人想知、冇人理、亦冇人爆料，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但公司一落TVB廣告助紂為虐，就會受到注意，醜聞就會被挖出嚟無限廣傳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73413228_483660285824159_1781793914622050304_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGJ7VD5-avOh6hLsKJSJQ1qgCixpdMjyARA-hTyeIX9Oo1elSDDij6k-CeALV0SFEDoFohVxLwd9roxQPOykFXAB_LyAO